    • Method Detail

      • fields

        public static Dns.ZoneListOption fields(Dns.ZoneField... fields)
        Returns an option to specify the zones's fields to be returned by the RPC call.

        If this option is not provided all zone fields are returned. ZoneOption.fields can be used to specify only the fields of interest. Zone ID is always returned, even if not specified. Dns.ZoneField provides a list of fields that can be used.

      • pageToken

        public static Dns.ZoneListOption pageToken(String pageToken)
        Returns an option to specify a page token.

        The page token (returned from a previous call to list) indicates from where listing should continue.

      • dnsName

        public static Dns.ZoneListOption dnsName(String dnsName)
        Restricts the list to only zone with this fully qualified domain name.

      • pageSize

        public static Dns.ZoneListOption pageSize(int pageSize)
        The maximum number of zones to return per RPC.

        The server can return fewer zones than requested. When there are more results than the page size, the server will return a page token that can be used to fetch other results.
